Validation of Cairns_Cooktowns EOMAP depth layers derived from Landsat and Sentinel vs acoustic validation data

This document shows linear regression plots between EOMAP depth layer derived from Landsat (EOMAP_Landsat) vs acoustic validation data and EOMAP depth layer derived from Sentinel (EOMAP_Sentinel) vs acoustic validation data. The figure below shows the location of acoustic validation data.
